SANSA RESOURCES
SANSA EO Catalogue
Satellite data over South and Southern Africa ranging with varying from 1.5m to 60m.
Higher resolution data have licence conditions attached, access to which can be discussed with SANSA.
https://climate.esa.int/en/odp/#/dashboard